Some complete cases are available are starting points at the web location:
https://portal.iter.org/departments/POP/CM/IMAS/SOLPS-ITER/
then inside the "Examples" folder.

The files contained in this directory are GIT version-controlled and thus only small addenda to the full cases above.

The set of switches necessary to add to a b2mn.dat file to reproduce 5.0 behaviour are given in the b2mn.dat.5.0 file.
The b2mn.dat.5.2 file contains the set of switches necessary to run the 5.2 model.

